      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but i dont want to wait weeks for a doctor appt just to ask something so basic. i've been reading that if your blood counts are stable and you feel healthy, you can taper off a bit to find your \"maintenance\" level. wouldn't it be pretty safe to just try the 2mg for a week and see how i feel? if i feel fine then i know it worked, right?",
